hadiths[28]{hadithnumber,text}:
3641,"Janab Kaseer bin Qais (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke main dimashq ki masjid mein Hazrat Abu-Darda (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas betha hua tha ke unke paas eik aadmi aaya aur usney kaha : aey Abu-Darda ! main eik hadees ki khatir madinatur-rasul se aap ki khidmat mein aaya hun. mujhey maloom hua hai ke aap usey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se bayan kartey hain. mujhey yahan uskey siwa aur koi kaam nahin hai. to unhoney kaha : beshak maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko suna hai farmatey they : ''jo shakhs kisi raastey mein husool ilm ki khatir chala ho, tu Allah taala usey jannat ki raahon mein se eik raah par chalaeyga. aur bila-shuba farishtey Talibe-ilm ki razamandi ke liye apney par bichhatey hain, aur sahibe-ilm ke liye aasmano mein basney waley, zameen mein rehney waley aur pani ke andar machliyan bhi maghfirat talab karti hain. aur bila-shuba aalim ki abid par fazilat aisey hi hai jaisey ke chaudahwin ke chaand ki sab sitaron par hoti hai, bila-shuba ulama anbiya ke waris hain aur anbiya ne koi dirham w Dinar wirsey mein nahin chhodey hain. unhoney ilm ki virasat chhodi hai. jisney usey hasil kar liya usney bada nasiba (wafir hissa) paya.''"
3642,"Usman bin abi Sauda ne Hazrat Abu-Darda (Raziallahu anhu) sey, unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se mazkura baala riwayat ke ham-maani bayan kya."
3643,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) ka bayan hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo koi ilm hasil kerney ke liye kisi raah par chalta hai tu Allah taala uski wajeh se uskey liye jannat ka raasta aasan farma deta hai. aur jisey uskey amal ne peechey rakha uska nasab usey aagey nahin badha sakta. ''"
3644,Janab ibne-abi namla apney walid ( Abu-Namla Ammar bin Muaz (Raziallahu anhu)) se riwayat kartey hain ke eik dafa wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke yahan bethey huey they aur eik yahudi bhi aap ke paas betha hua tha ke eik janaza guzra . usney puchha : aey Muhammad ! kya ye ( maiyat ( bolti hai? Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah hi behtar janta hai.'' yahudi ne kaha : ye bolti hai. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' ehle-kitab jo tumhen bayan keren tum uski tasdeeq karo na takzeeb . balke yun kaho : ham Allah aur uskey Rasulon par emaan laye . agar unki baat ghalat hui to tum ne ( goya ( uski tasdeeq nahin ki aur agar sach hui to usey jhutlaya nahin hoga .''
3645,"Hazrat Zaid bin Sabit (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mujhey hukm diya to maine yahudiyon ki tehreer seekh li. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah ki qasam! yahudiyon se jo main likhwata hun us par mujhey aitimaad nahin hai.'' chunanche maine (unki zaban likhna padhna) seekh li, aur do haftey na guzrey ke main us mein khoob mahir ho gaya. phir aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko jab kuch likhna hota to main hi likha karta. aur jab koi khat waghera aata to aap ko padh kar sunata tha."
3646,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr bin al-Aas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se manqul hai, wo kehtey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se main jo kuch sunta wo sab likh liya karta tha taake usey hifz kar lun . to ( baaz ( qureshiyon ne mujhey mana kya. unhoney kaha : to her baat , jo sunta hai, likh leta hai, halanke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) eik insan hain ghussay aur khushi ( dono haalaton ( mein guftgu kartey hain, to maine likhna moquf kar diya aur ye baat Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se arz ki . to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne apney dehane-mubarak ki taraf ungli se ishara kartey huey farmaya : ''likha karo, qasam us zaat ki jiskey haath mein meri jaan hai! is se siwaye haq ke aur kuch nikalta hi nahin hai.''"
3647,"Mattalib bin Abdullah bin Hantab se manqul hai ke Hazrat Zaid bin Sabit (Raziallahu anhu), Hazrat Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) ke yahan aaye to unhoney un se eik hadees ke baarey mein poochha. to Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) ne eik shakhs se kaha ke usey likh lo, to Hazrat Zaid bin Sabit (Raziallahu anhu) ne un se kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne hamen hukm diya tha ke ham unki koi hadees zabt tehreer mein na laeyn. chunanche unhoney usey mita diya."
3648,Hazrat abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke ham tashahud aur Quran ke ilawa kuch na likha kartey they.
3649,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke jab Makka Fateh hua to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) khadey huey . aur aap ke khutbey ka zikr kya. to ehle-Yamen ka eik aadmi khada hua , uska naam Abu-Shah tha, usney kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! ye mujhey likh diijiye. to aapney farmaya : '' Abu-Shah ko likh do.''"
3650,Waleed (bin Mazeed) ne kaha ke maine abu-Amr ( Auzaai (Rahimahullah) ( se puchha ke usney kya chiz likhwaai thi ? unhoney kaha ke wohi khutba jo usney us roz aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se suna tha.
3651,"Janab Aamir bin Abdullah bin Zuber apney walid se riwayat kartey hain, wo kehtey hain ke maine apney walid Hazrat Zuber (bin Awaam) (Raziallahu anhu) se arz kya ke aap ko kya cheez rukawat hai ke aap Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se is tarah ahadis bayan nahin kartey jaisey ke aap ke deegar sathi bayan kartey hain? unhoney kaha : Allah ki qasam ! mujhey aap ke yahan bahut hi qadr w manzilat hasil thi. lekin maine aap ko farmatey huey suna hai : ''jisney mujh par jaan-boojh kar jhoot bola usey chahiye ke apna thikana jahannam mein bana ley.''"
3652,"Hazrat Jundub (bin Abdullah bijli ( (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' jisney apni raey se kitabullah main kuch kaha, chahey durust hi kaha ho, to bhi usney khata ki.''"
3653,"Janab abu-Salaam (Mamtur al-Habshi) se manqul hai, usney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke eik khaadim se naqal kya ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab koi baat kartey to apni baat ko teen baar dohratey. (sharae masla apney sunne waley ko khoob samjhatey.)"
3654,"Hazrat Urwa (Rahimahullah) bayan kartey hain ke Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) ummul-momenin Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) ke hujrey ke pehlu mein bethey jabkey wo Namaz padh rahi thin . Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) kehney lagey : aey hujrey wali ! suniye . do baar kaha . jab unhoney apni Namaz puri kar li to kaha : kya tumhen us shakhs par aur uski baaton par tajjub nahin aata , yaqinan Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) baat kartey to agar koi (aap ke alfaz) shumar karna chahta to shumar kar sakta tha."
3655,"Hazrat Urwa bin Zuber se manqul hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki zauja mohtarma ummul-momenin Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha : kya tumhen Abu-Huraira par tajjub nahin aata ke wo aaye aur merey hujrey ke paas beth kar mujhey sunaney ko , Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki hadisein bayan kerney lagey, jabkey main nawaafil padh rahi thi, aur phir merey Namaz mukammal kerney se pehley hi uth kar chal diye. agar main unhen paati to main unhen batati ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) tumhari tarah tez tez baaten nahin kya kartey they."
3656,Hazrat Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mughaalton se mana farmaya hai.
3657,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jisey kisi mufti ne ilm ke baghair fatwa diya to amal kerney waley ka gunah fatwa deney waley par hoga.'' Suleman Mehri ki riwayat mein mazeed hai : ''jisney apney bhai ko koi aisa mashwara diya jabkey usey ilm tha ke bhalai uskey khilaf mein hai to usney uski khayanat ki.'' ye lafz Suleman ke hain."
3658,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jis se ilm ki baat puchhi gaee aur usney usey chupa liya (aur bataya nahin) tu Allah taala qiyamat ke roz usey aag ki lagaam dega.''"
3659,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) ne bayan kya, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum (mujh sey) suntey ho aur tum se suna jaeyga aur phir jo tum se sunega us se suna jaeyga.''"
3660,"Hazrat Zaid bin Sabit (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko suna, aap farmatey they : ''Allah taala us shakhs ko khush w khurram aur shadab rakhey jisney ham se koi baat suni phir usey hifz kya aur yaad rakha taake usey pahunchaey, bahut se ilm w fiqh ka ilm rakhney waley apney se badh kar ziyada daana (samajhdar) aur faqeeh logon ko pahunchatey hain, aur bahut se ilm w fiqh ka ilm rakhney waley aisey hotey hain jo dar-haqiqat daana aur faqeeh nahin hotey .''"
3661,Hazrat Sehal bin Saad (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''qasam Allah ki! Allah azz-w-jall teri rehnumai se kisi eik shakhs ko bhi raahe-haq dikha dey to ye terey liye surkh oonton se afzal hai.''
3662,Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''bani Israel (ehle-kitab) se riwayat kar saktey ho us mein koi harj nahin.''
3663,Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu Anhuma) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) (kabhi-kabhi) hamen Bani-Israel ki baaten bayan kartey rehtey yahan tak ke subh ho jati aur phir Namaz ke khayal hi se uthtey .
3664,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' jisney Allah ki razamandi wala ilm is gharz se hasil kya ke duniya hasil karey, to aisa aadmi qiyamat ke din jannat ki khushbu nahin pa sakega .''"
3665,"Hazrat Auf bin Malik Ashjai (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se suna, aap farmatey they : ''waaz wohi kahega jo ameer ho ya uski taraf se muqarrar kya gaya ho ya koi apni badai ya shekhi ka izhar kerney wala hoga.''"
3666,"Hazrat abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke main gharib muhajrin ki majlis mein ja betha. wo log libas mein tangi ki bina par uriyaan ho janey ke dar se eik doosrey ki ot mein bethey huey they aur eik qaari ham par padh raha tha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) tashrif ley aaye aur bhari majlis mein khadey ho gaey . jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) khadey huey to qaari khamosh ho gaya , to aapney salam kya aur puchha : ''tum kya kar rahey they ?'' ham ne kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! qaari padh raha tha aur ham Allah taala ki kitab sun rahey they. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''hamd hai us Allah ki jisney meri ummat mein aisey log paida kiye jinkey baarey mein mujhey hukm diya gaya hai ke main apney aap ko unke sath rokey rakhun.'' chunanche Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) hamarey darmiyan mein beth gaey taake apney aap ko hamarey barabar Sabit karen. phir aapney apney haath se ishara kya to unhoney halqa bana liya aur un sab ke chehrey aap ke samney aagey. abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain ke main nahin samajhta ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne merey siwa kisi ko pehchana ho. phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''aey muhajrin ke faqir logo! tumhen qiyamat ke roz kamil Noor ki bashaarat ho. tum log maldaron se aadha din pehley jannat mein dakhil hogey aur uski miqdaar paanch so saal hai.''"
3667,Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo log namaze-Fajr se Suraj nikalney tak Allah ka zikr keren mujhey unke sath bethey rehna ziyada pasand hai us se ke aulade-Ismail se chaar ghulam azad karun. aur main aisey logon ke sath betha rahun jo namaze-Asr se Suraj ghuroob honey tak Allah ka zikr keren ziyada pasandida hai us se ke chaar ghulam azad karun.''
3668,Hazrat Abdullah (bin Masood) (Raziallahu anhu) ka bayan hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mujhey farmaya : '' mujh par sura nisaa ki qirat karo.'' maine arz kya : main aap par padhun? halanke ( Quran (aap par nazil hua hai. aapney farmaya : ''main doosrey se sunna chahta hun. chunanche maine qirat ki yahan tak ke jab main aayat kareema ( فَكَيْفَ إِذَا جِئْنَا مِنْ كُلِّ أُمَّةٍ بِشَهِيدٍ . . .) par pahuncha to maine apna sar uthaya to dekha ke aap ki aankhen aansuon se beh rahi thin.
